180103 : old teleportation stuff

\skill{Ability cost 30xp ccf 1.5 "Psychic Teleportation":} The character can teleport within his vision to an empty square to which he has a clear undisturbed line of sight. The maximum distance is equal to 3$\cdot$psy. The character can spend mana to gain longer distance at cost +2/m.

Teleporting costs 2 mana and is a full round action. The character cannot do anything else, or move faster than maneuver.

Clear line of sight is blocked by monsters of same or larger size. Clear line of sight can be acquired with the "gapfinder" ability if otherwise blocked.

Upgrades : \\
cost +10xp: lvl 2 allows to teleport in 2a. \\
cost +20xp: lvl 3 allows to teleport in 1a.  \\
cost +20xp: cheap teleport costs only 1 mana.


\skill{Ability cost 30xp ccf 1.5 "Strenuous Teleportation":} The character can teleport to any empty square to which he has clear undisturbed line of sight. Teleporting is a full round action and costs 2 stamina. The user cannot move faster than maneuver or do anything else.

Clear line of sight is blocked by monsters of same or larger size. Clear line of sight can be acquired with the "gapfinder" ability if otherwise blocked.

Upgrades: \\
cost +10xp: lvl 2 allows teleportation in 2a. \\
cost +20xp: lvl 3 allows teleportation in 1a. \\
cost +20xp: cheap teleport costs only 1 stamina.


\skill{Maneuver "Running teleport":} Running teleport counts as upgrade for Psychic Teleportation and Strenuous Teleportation. \\
lvl 1 cost +10xp allows for walking when teleporting via P.T. or S.T. \\
lvl 2 cost +10xp allows for running when teleporting via P.T. or S.T. \\
lvl 3 cost +10xp allows for dashing when teleporting via P.T. or S.T.












